author: James Ellingworth, Associated Press
title: Sainz crash ends 3rd practice session in Russia
text: Photo: Ivan Sekretarev, AP Course marshals remove the crashed car of Toro Rosso driver Carlos Sainz Jr. of Spain during the third free practice at the 'Sochi Autodrom' Formula One circuit in Sochi, Russia, on Saturday, Oct. 10, 2015. A heavy crash for Carlos Sainz Jr. ended the final practice session at the Russian Grand Prix on Saturday with the Toro Rosso driver hospitalized. The Formula one race will be held on Sunday. SOCHI, Russia (AP) — A heavy crash for Carlos Sainz Jr. ended the final practice session at the Russian Grand Prix on Saturday with the Toro Rosso driver flown to hospital.
